  "detailed_description": "Dynamic Shooting VR is the ultimate practical shooting simulator! Compete across different ranges with captivating themes and challenging parkours. Experience intense gameplay with fine tuned weapon mechanics. Become a champion marksman. Are you ready for the thrill?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/d67644e7f79b4955267a993e0bb13057.poster.avif?t=1708373858\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/d67644e7f79b4955267a993e0bb13057.webm?t=1708373858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/d67644e7f79b4955267a993e0bb13057.mp4?t=1708373858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>No motion sickness, very comfortable VR experience! You may play sitting or standing!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/b3bb7215b978c9042d4ac9716f942c09.poster.avif?t=1708373858\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/b3bb7215b978c9042d4ac9716f942c09.webm?t=1708373858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/b3bb7215b978c9042d4ac9716f942c09.mp4?t=1708373858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Shooting ranges with various themes, targets and weapons. Yes, we have Western!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/966f9719461f036d012cfbc876083e37.poster.avif?t=1708373858\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/966f9719461f036d012cfbc876083e37.webm?t=1708373858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549600/extras/966f9719461f036d012cfbc876083e37.mp4?t=1708373858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Perfect for party playing with your family and friends. Compete with your friends with your highscores!</strong><br><br>We still have ranges and guns under development for the future releases, stay tuned for more!",
